		1. Officially licensed by Sauber F1 Team, the model is an intricate replica of the original Sauber's &quot;2024 F1 Race car C44&quot; driven by Finnish Driver
		Valtteri Bottas and  Chinese F1 driver Zhou Guanyu;
		2, Proportional speed control using remote controller;
		3, Replication of aerodynamic features on the real F1 car including the Aggressive bodywork and floor, and the Red Bull-style radiator inlets;
		4, Full printed logos of the sponsors' Logos on the body of the car;
		5. Wider back tires to provide a more realistic look that replicates the real car
